question.answer: Well, honestly, it was either TR or TB, and since I really didn't like the idea of getting the 'ol consumption, I thought I'd give TR a try.
I drink a lot of tea and I like to take baths (I'm actually an old woman who has a great plastic sugeon). I especially like books, like when I get to throw them at other old people.
Seriously, it's a toss up between George Gershwin's Rhapsody in Blue, and Frank Zappa's Don't eat the Yellow Snow.
Until I feel I've gotten everything pretty much figured out
By being attacked by dogs that spit flaming glass
